name: Foolin Around Slot (East)
description:
Introduction

Possibly the most underrated canyon in Northwash. Stemming for hundreds of feet, high-stemming, one R silo xing and one R+ silo xing are all available to those who wish to practice for the big leagues. All the hard stuff is optional, but taking the easy way through is no walk in the park. A mandatory swimmer at the end. Wetsuit not required, except in winter.

Approach

Descent

Exit

A couple Class 4 short moves. Short and fun exit scramble up a gulley and a quick cross-country hike.
